CustomProperties.Name: AutomaticallyClose
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to toggle the functionality of closing the date picker when the desired date range is selected.

CustomProperties.Name: CalendarRowHeight
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to adjust the calendar row height to fit specific needs

CustomProperties.Name: CalendarHeight
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to define the height for the component.

CustomProperties.Name: IconOnSelect
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set what happens when the calendar icon is selected.

CustomProperties.Name: Required
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to toggle if the form is required.

CustomProperties.Name: PrimaryOrange
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to toggle the primary color of the date input control.

CustomProperties.Name: onChange
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set the onChange behavior.
